Expert Viewpoint: The Pivotal Role of Domain Names

The significance of a powerful domain name cannot be overstated.

With over two decades of experience in the industry, Michael, the founder of OnlineBusiness.com has witnessed firsthand the transformative impact that the right domain name can have on the trajectory of a business.

One illustrative example is the journey of I-Newswire.com, a company Michael led, that underwent a remarkable transformation.

When the opportunity arose to acquire their best domain name, Newswire.com, a strategic decision was made that defined the company's future.

Through rebranding and upgrading to Newswire.com, the business experienced exponential growth. This pivotal move not only enhanced the brand's credibility but also attracted a wider audience.

It is a testament to the fact that domain names are not merely addresses on the internet; they are digital assets that hold the power to shape the destiny of an online business.

Why RankBio.com is a Valuable Domain Name

RankBio.com is a valuable name because of several reasons. For one, it is a unique online asset and only one RankBio.com exists in the entire world. Yes, there are variations of this domain that exists or that can be registered but there is only one RankBio.com. Because of this fact using this for your online business can help you stand out and gain credibility and trust.

RankBio.com is years old and that means it's aged which is a big plus in the eyes of the search engines. So naturally you will want to optimize your website for the search engines and having an aged domain is a big advantage.

Related to age is a domain's MOZ DA (Domain Authority) value. MOZ.com is an SEO tool and resource site that is one of the most highly respected and popular sites amongst online business owners and marketers. The higher the DA score the better. In simple terms the DA score is a reflection of the popularity of the website/domain using links as the measurement.

RankBio.com has a DA score of 21 which is a great start, considering we have not done any SEO to this domain.
